          "instructions": {
            "summary": "In PingOne, each OAuth application (Admin app and Customer app) must list its redirect URI exactly — same scheme, host, and path. You can register **multiple** URIs per app (e.g. **localhost** for dev and **https://api.pingdeme.org** for a hosted BFF) so the same tenant works in every environment.",
            "steps": [
